Method behavioural specifications:
- The integer 2D array parameter `grid` must not be null.
- The integer 2D array parameter `grid` must be a square matrix of size `n x n`.
- All elements in the diagonals of the integer 2D array parameter `grid` must be non-zero.
- All elements in the integer 2D array parameter `grid` that are not in the diagonals must be 0.
- The boolean result is true if the integer 2D array parameter `grid` is an X-Matrix.
- The boolean result is false if the integer 2D array parameter `grid` is not an X-Matrix.